text: Đura Sentđerđi (1900–1980) was a Yugoslav swimmer. He competed in the men's 400 metre freestyle event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:1980 deaths Category:Serbian male swimmers Category:Yugoslav male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Yugoslavia Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sombor
